[SHORT DESC]
Summons permanent sun. 
[LONG DESC]
<p>When this Pokémon is brought out, a permanent sun covers the battlefield. It can only be removed by bringing out a Pokémon with Drizzle, Sand Stream, or Snow Warning, or by using Rain Dance, Sandstorm, or Hail. When two or more Pokémon with any of the weather abilities switch in at the same time, the slower Pokémon's ability will take place.</p>